| x | (FRONT) |
| x x | (FRONTLEFT and FRONTRIGHT) |
| x O x | (LEFT and RIGHT) |
| x x | (BACKLEFT and BACKRIGHT) |
| x | (BACK) |
--------------------------------------------
| Legend: |
| [O] = Target |
| [x] = available Slot |
--------------------------------------------
